---
title: Hoisin-Glazed Steak with Scallion Rice, Ponzu Green Beans & Sriracha Mayo
description: One of our favorite ways to add tons of flavor to any protein in mere minutes? Whipping up a delectable glaze. Here, we blend tangy, barbecue-like hoisin sauce with aromatic garlic powder, then pour the mixture over steak during the last few minutes of cooking for deliciously sticky-sweet results. More of the glaze is drizzled over the steak just before serving for good measure; then, it’s all paired with fluffy rice, ponzu roasted green beans, and spicy mayo. Now THAT’S what we call a winning dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/hoisin-glazed-steak-f906b01a.jpg
